label: cityName
comment: Name of the city corresponding to this observation.

label: powerDistributionDivision
comment: The name of the power distribution division corresponding to this observation.

label: powerDistributionSubdivision
comment: The name of the sub division in the power distribution  corresponding to this observation.

label: powerDistributionSection
comment: The name of the power distribution section corresponding to this observation.

label: areaServed
comment: The list of geographic areas (states, districts) served by the entity.

label: category
comment: Represents the name of classification of an entity or service based on a particular aspect.

label: categoryCode
comment: The code of the category corresponding to this observation.

label: totalServiceCount
comment: The total count of services availed corresponding to this observation.

label: billedServicesCount
comment: The total count of services that are billed corresponding to this observation.

label: energyConsumption
comment: Energy consumed over a specific time corresponding to this observation.

label: powerConsumption
comment: Power consumed by the entity corresponding to this observation.
